Installing Zeppelin:

```cd ~/hadoop
```wget https://dlcdn.apache.org/zeppelin/zeppelin-0.10.1/zeppelin-0.10.1-bin-netinst.tgz```
```tar zeppelin-0.10.1-bin-netinst.tgz```
```cd ~/hadoop/zeppelin-0.10.1-bin-netinst/
```bin/zeppelin-daemon.sh start```
Go to browser and search "localhost:8080"

When done with zeppelin:
```bin/zeppelin-daemon.sh stop```
Reference: https://zeppelin.apache.org/docs/latest/quickstart/install.html#building-zeppelin-from-source
